				<td colspan="2"><span>As I approach into higher levels (currently 49) I am aware that certain mobs will summon you and you essentially go running back within melee range of them.
<br />

<br />
I'm not too keen on this idea.  I'm also not sure what sort of beasts do summon, as I understand it, they must be at least level 51+   Can any mob &gt;51 summon?  I'm considering trying my luck soloing in 'the grey' in another level or two and would like to get a heads up on this first.
<br />

<br />
Thanks gang.
<br />

<br />
</span></td>
